data.description: This beautiful home has all the features you have been waiting for. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms downstairs, there's a bonus room with a full bathroom on the second level. Kitchen offers plenty of counterspace with a breakfast nook and dining area overlooking the spacious living room. There is tile flooring throughout the home with the exception of upstairs and a screened-in porch overlooking the pond. A Community Clubhouse with pool, playground, basketball court and tennis court is just some of the great amenities in the neighborhood with a low HOA fee. HVAC is 6 years old and the roof was replaced in 2022. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fabulous home. Call today to schedule a tour!
